Struct ColorKey

Define a color key to build the color scale. It defines a Color at a relative position within the scale (% from first color in scale).

Compare(ColorKey, ColorKey)

Allow a comparison of two color keys based on their relative position withtin the scale. x is greater than y if its relative position is greater than y relative position. Compliant with Comparison<T> delegate for list sorting.
